---
title: Homestyle Creamy Chicken Stew with Cheddar Chive Biscuits
description: Better than grandma's biscuits? We'd say so, but don't tell her! You'll be serving up ultimate comfort tonight with a chicken stew topped with out-of-this-world cheddar and chive biscuits. A creamy base and lots of green peas make this stew nostalgic and satisfying.
